<p><span class="anchor" id="p23"></span>فَبِأَيِّ آلاءِ رَبِّكُما تُكَذِّبانِ <span class="c2">(٣٠)</span><a href="#p23" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
